data.description: Outstanding home in the stylish Kolbe Farms community conveniently located just a short distance to City Centre, Memorial City & The Galleria. Located by the community entrance with manned security just steps from your front door from 6pm to 6am daily for an added layer of security! This 3 story townhome is just a short walk to the pool and features a great interior with high ceilings, abundant natural light and popular floor plan. Secondary bedroom with en-suite bath on first level, built-in book cases in foyer and hardwood floors. Second level kitchen/dining/living area with 12' ceilings, balcony overlooking the front entrance & large kitchen with walk-in pantry. Center island and abundant counter space and cabinets. 3rd level features primary suite with hardwood floors, bath with separate shower and oversized tub and dual vanities. 3rd bedroom suite with attached bath also located on 3rd level along with laundry room. Sun filled and bright roof top terrace on 4th level!
